{"tid":1746781,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"林夕逾3000作品被消失","createTime":"2019-11-23T02:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T06:20:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9168c943e919e95e1d3c3255f99daad94016b5e0","tid":1746781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191123/20811773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191123%2F20811773&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=eb432bb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191123%2F20811773&h=27387c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191123/20811773</a><br />\n<br />\n林夕逾3000作品被消失<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191123/large/1574430475_b853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191123%2Flarge%2F1574430475_b853.jpg&h=ae479854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林夕剛於周日在台北出席集會，在台上訴說香港現況。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n填詞人林夕剛於周日到台北出席「撐香港，要自由音樂會」，在台上講述香港警方現時狀況，又力數香港政府破壞法治。昨日有消息指，林夕逾3,000首填詞作品均被內地封殺。有內地網民更指已接到通知，林夕的所有作品會在內地音樂網下架。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》昨翻查多個內地音樂網，發現在搜尋欄目輸入「林夕」的名字後，均出現「沒有搜尋到相關歌曲」，即使以林夕2008年為北京奧運會填詞的主題曲《北京歡迎你》，以及其他名作如王菲的《紅豆》、楊千嬅的《再見二丁目》以及張國榮的《左右手》等歌名來搜尋，亦無一幸免。據知，林夕至今填詞作品已超過3,000首，對於其作品在內地音樂網被消失，網民反應不一，有人留言指「歌單全軍覆沒」、「直接刪除詞作者信息就行」，但亦有人留言「活該」、「禁吧禁吧都禁了最好。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：克己 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n阿澤嘲港警唔識食"},{"pid":"348d6ea75929d8f5dcf9471aaa012501451efe8c","tid":1746781,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:12:45.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=3d61fa48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=73752fdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"4266a96c163d882524265ae71737a7810962eb15","tid":1746781,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:14:04.000Z","msg":"北京歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=